# The worker build receives an explicit allowlist. In particular, never send
# operator credentials, Git history, local runs, caches, or virtualenvs to the
# Docker daemon as build-context data.
**

!pyproject.toml
!uv.lock
!README.md

!src/
!src/**

!configs/
!configs/**

!datasets/
!datasets/releases/
!datasets/releases/**

!docker/
!docker/mem0-worker.Dockerfile
!docker/core-worker.Dockerfile
!docker/amem-worker.Dockerfile
!docker/memos-worker.Dockerfile
!docker/locks/
!docker/locks/**
!docker/wheelhouse/
!docker/wheelhouse/**

# Operator credentials and mutable execution state never enter a build context.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
data/
runs/
*.key
*.pem
